includedIn.synopsis: An award-winning ensemble including Jessica Lange, Sarah Paulson, Evan Peters and Lady Gaga play an ever-changing cast of characters in this superbly creepy anthology series from Nip/Tuck and Glee creator Ryan Murphy.
